rdfs:label: M2M
ns:common.topic.description:
MMT is the Eclipse implementation of the OMG QVT standard. MMT is a subproject of Eclipse Modeling Project.
Three components are available for model to model transformations:
ATL from INRIA
Procedural QVT, from Borland
Declarative QVT, from Obeo
Implementations announced by Obeo and Borland should be available in the near future.

ns:common.document.text: M2M is the Eclipse implementation of the OMG QVT standard (the Eclipse foundation is now a member of OMG as of January 2007).
